        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 21 at 3:50AM MDT until August 21 at 4:45AM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>SVRGGW

The National Weather Service in Glasgow has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Southeastern McCone County in northeastern Montana...
North central Prairie County in northeastern Montana...
Southwestern Dawson County in northeastern Montana...

* Until 445 AM MDT.

* At 350 AM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 16 miles southeast
of Brockway, or 20 miles south of Circle, moving east at 40 mph.

HAZARD...Half dollar size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Glendive, West Glendive, Lindsay, Bloomfield, Stipek, and Forest
Park.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
